<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <title>Branduri | Luxury Bags by Octavia</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Branduri Luxury Bags by Octavia">
    <%- include("../fragmente/head") %>
</head>
<body id="top">
    <%- include("../fragmente/header") %>

    <main>
        <section class="zona">
            <h2>Branduri</h2>
            <p>Aceasta pagina poate gazdui prezentari pentru brandurile premium din showroom, cu descrieri, origini si linii reprezentative.</p>
            <p>Meniul este identic cu cel din celelalte pagini pentru a respecta cerinta de navigare comuna in tot site-ul.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="zona">
            <h2>Comparatie branduri premium</h2>
            <div class="container-tabel-responsive">
                <table class="tabel-responsive tabel-branduri-normal">
                    <caption>Branduri de lux si caracteristici utile pentru alegerea unei genti</caption>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Brand</th>
                            <th>Model reprezentativ</th>
                            <th>Stil</th>
                            <th>Materiale frecvente</th>
                            <th>Recomandat pentru</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Chanel</td>
                            <td>Classic Flap</td>
                            <td>Elegant, atemporal</td>
                            <td>Piele matlasata, lant metalic</td>
                            <td>Tinute de seara si colectii iconice</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Hermes</td>
                            <td>Birkin</td>
                            <td>Lux discret, exclusivist</td>
                            <td>Piele premium, finisaje manuale</td>
                            <td>Investitie si aparitii rafinate</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Dior</td>
                            <td>Lady Dior</td>
                            <td>Feminin, sofisticat</td>
                            <td>Cannage, piele fina, charms</td>
                            <td>Evenimente elegante si tinute romantice</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Prada</td>
                            <td>Galleria</td>
                            <td>Modern, urban</td>
                            <td>Piele saffiano, linii curate</td>
                            <td>Birou, city look si purtare zilnica</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include("../fragmente/footer") %>
</body>
</html>
